Endpoint.description: The Endpoint schema defines the properties of an Endpoint resource.  It represents the properties of an entity that sends or receives protocol defined messages over a transport.
Endpoint.longDescription: This resource shall be used to represent a fabric endpoint for a Redfish implementation.
